Detailed Description

Structure used to store state information needed to delete an already scheduled timer entry.

An instance of this structure must be passed to cvmx_tim_add_entry in order to be able to delete an entry later with cvmx_tim_delete_entry.

NOTE: This structure should be considered opaque by the application, and the application should not access its members
